Body:
Description: Hello, 

When trying to do client Agent software upgrade from EPP, it fails to do so on 10 machines out of the 50. 

Can you please assist? 
I can arrange a remote session with the customer if you want to. 


Kind Regards 
Kostas Mousmoulis
Invitation updated. Attendees: No attendees listed
Invitation updated. Attendees: Andre Le Roux, Kostas Mousmoulis
Invitation updated. Attendees: Andre Le Roux

What We've Learned Updated: The EPP Server IP address was lost from the EPP client, it is not known how this could have happened unfortunately the logs were not enabled and thus minimizes the ability to investigate the root cause.

Next Steps Updated: The EPPSetServer tool was used to resolve the issue.  The customer will use the tool on the remaining 9 endpoint computers that are affected and then give us a status update afterward.
